targets.query: SELECT "value"  *8 FROM "udpStats" WHERE ("port_id" >= ${gold_portrange_min} AND flow_id<>'20000' AND "port_id" < ${gold_portrange_min}+${flowcount}) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "flow_id"
